data.description: Immaculate 3 bedroom, 2 bath single-story located in   Stablewood Farms. Spacious open floor plan with a large dining room, study and  tons of  natural light and soaring ceilings. Pride of ownership shows with  beautiful  wood-like luxury vinyl flooring,  gourmet island silestone kitchen with abundant cabinet space and 42" cabinets.  Large primary suite with walk-in closet and spa-like bath with soaking  tub and separate shower.  Backyard  oasis with a  covered patio,  pool and  hot tub to enjoy during those hot Texas summers.  Stablewood Farms is a family community zoned to award winning Cy Fair ISD with  tons of amenities including a neighborhood pool, splash pad, and  parks.  PRIME  location with easy access to TX-99, Highway 249 and  Hwy 290.  Minutes  from  restaurants, shopping,  entertainment and hospitals.    Low taxes and never flooded!
